nodes.text: D5-F2 was an astromech droid that served the reconstituted Sith Empire aboard Vaiken Spacedock and, later, Crag Outpost during the Galactic War with the Galactic Republic.
D5-F2 appears in the video game Star Wars: The Old Republic: Rise of the Hutt Cartel as the Imperial mission courier for Oricon, a Daily Area added in Game Update 2.4
